              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MCPLT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two micro-channel plate detectors upstream",
                "of the ionization chamber measured the local time",
                "of flight of the recoils over a distance of 60 cm"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Recoils were detected in DRAGON focal plane",
                "using a ionization chamber with four segments, which",
                "provided energy loss and residual energy (dE-E)",
                "information. Chamber was filled with isobutane at",
                "a typical pressure of 8 Torr."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BGO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gas target was surrounded by an array of",
                "30 BGO gamma ray detectors."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Windowless He gas target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Recoils were identified by energy loss",
                "and time of flight method. It was possible to",
                "distinguish beam particles from reaction",
                "products. Coincidence between BGO array and ionization",
                "chamber reduced the background."
              ]
            }
